name: Suggestions
description: Have users submit suggestions to help improve some things.
end_user_data_statement: This cog stores data provided by users for the express purpose of submitting suggestions. It does not store user data which was not provided through a command. Users may remove their own content without making a data removal request. This cog does not support data requests, but will respect deletion requests.
install_msg: Thank you for installing Suggestions. Load the cog with `[p]load suggestions`.
author: NoobInDaHause
